Saute beef in a bit of oil till browned.  Add mushrooms & onions & cook till very soft.  Add remaining ingredients & simmer till
meat is tender, at least 2 hours.  Taste & adjust seasonings. Serve over rice, noodles or potatoes.
Serving size is 3/4 c. for 2 oz protein + 1/4 c. cooked vegetable.
